name: Conquer my smile
description: Elias Scardovelli, I've been a Plastic Artist since 1984, I went through several stages, I've sold 4,500 works, but I was fascinated with this world of digital art. I followed for a long time and now I decided to participate as an artist. This work portrays a happy person, perhaps because she conquered the construction of the factory she wanted so much to have. I graduated in Arts, Designer and Engineer. I started to paint before studying, I was Nife, I don't know if I still am. Width 13134pix, Height 5852pix, 9.62MB.
